  <para>Appendix 5 has illustrations for encoding orthodontic/craniofacial
  views using DICOM with SNOMED CT terminology. If needed, more SNOMED CT
  codes can be retrieved from the Unified Medical Language Systems
  Metathesaurus browser on the US National Library of Medicine website (<link
  xlink:href="https://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/index.html">https://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/index.html</link>).</para>

